<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Inspection Report</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Inspection Report Generated</h2>
    
    <p>Hello,</p>
    
    <p>An inspection report has been generated for the following job:</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p><strong>Job ID:</strong> <%= jobId %></p>
        <p><strong>FHA Number:</strong> <%= jobData.fha_number %></p>
        <p><strong>Inspection Type:</strong> <%= jobData.inspection_type %></p>
        <p><strong>Property Address:</strong> <%= jobData.address %></p>
        <p><strong>Inspector:</strong> <%= jobData.inspector_name %></p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> <%= jobData.status %></p>
    </div>
    
    <p>The detailed inspection report is attached to this email as a PDF file.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    Art Neidich Team</p>
</body>
</html> 